animeTitle: Eureka Seven AO: Jungfrau no Hanabana-tachi
animeDescription: An original video anime, released on Blu-ray in a combined Hybrid Disc that also hold an Eureka Seven AO game for the PlayStation 3.   The OVA is set between episodes eight and nine of the series.
